{"tid":1056277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（人唔笑狗都吠）深圳大學校長：容許學生有自由的政治信仰，不會強迫，無需要擔心學術自由受限制。","createTime":"2019-03-11T05:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T05:49:47.000Z","uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2e56d9b0658bc3709cc42c682b35b43abf3e80","tid":1056277,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:44:08.000Z","msg":"深圳大學校長李清泉表，目前香港的「一周一行」措施，對內地學者來港學術交流帶來不便，希望能掃除障礙。李清泉在北京接受訪問時指，內地稅制令到內地授課的香港教師要支付較高稅率，同樣應該拆牆鬆綁。<br />\n<br />\n大灣區規劃綱要提出，鼓勵港澳青年到內地升學。李清泉建議，設立專項獎學金鼓勵香港學生到內地讀大學，認為內地大學的學術設施比得上香港，容許學生有自由的政治信仰，不會強迫，無需要擔心學術自由受限制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1074827&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1074827%26csid%3D261_341&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FJmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=d9dd7b62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1074827&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a1c08aeaa6d3d946a395fe6c6f6c7f08b0b61167","tid":1056277,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"有自由到咁樣都得？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.epochweekly.com/402/60-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.epochweekly.com%2F402%2F60-01.jpg&h=4a9f1640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/images-epochhk-com/20051121-a2-1@1200x1200.jpg?url=http://images.epochhk.com/20051121/a2-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2Fimages-epochhk-com%2F20051121-a2-1%401200x1200.jpg%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fimages.epochhk.com%2F20051121%2Fa2-1.jpg&h=89341b6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1448cef52319d12b241287c62dc86822093d53f4","tid":1056277,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"吹水